                ivec3_t N=(Nx,Ny,Nz) decide the BZ grid {k}
                    each k_i is an irrep.
                We also need a reciprocal lattice grid {G}
                    All G_i such that G_i^2 = G_i*M*G_i < Emax;
                        M is the inverse metrix tensor.
